Installation
============
git clone git://github.com/ollie/highway.git
cd highway
bundle install

Running the game
================
ruby example.rb
ruby example.rb -m maps/002.txt
ruby example.rb -p 19,7
ruby example.rb -m maps/002.txt -p 19,7
ruby example.rb --map=maps/002.txt
ruby example.rb --pos=19,7
ruby example.rb --map=maps/002.txt --pos=19,7

